@startuml RDI-AgentX-Architecture
title AgentBeats Competition - Benchmark Flow\n//<color:gray>(How does evaluation work?)</color>//

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor<<Assessee>> #E8D5F2
    BackgroundColor<<Assessor>> #C8E6C9
}

skinparam packageStyle rectangle

' High-level actors
component "Purple Agents\n(Under Test)" as Purple <<Assessee>>
component "Green Agent\n(Assessor)" as Green <<Assessor>>

' Main benchmark flow
Purple -right-> Green : 1. traces
Green -down-> Green : 2. evaluate
Green -up-> Purple : 4. scores

note bottom of Purple
  **Coordination Patterns**
  ──────────────────
  Hub-Spoke: C ↔ R1, R2
  Chain: P1 → P2 → P3
  Mesh: All ↔ All
end note

note bottom of Green
  **Evaluation Tiers (Plugins)**
  ──────────────────
  Tier 1: Graph metrics
  Tier 2: LLM + Latency
  Tier 3: Custom Plugins (BaseEvaluator)
end note

@enduml
